query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mk t) NoHashJoin(mk t mi_idx) NoMergeJoin(mi_idx mk t ci) */ select count(*)
from movie_keyword AS mk
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005 AND t.kind_id = 1
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info_type_id = 101
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id;
